    Class Description
    AbstractEdge
    An AbstractEdge that is the edge of a Node.
    ActionsRating
    Class representing a rating for all possible PlayerAction values.
    AffectedEdgesLookUpTable
    provides a Look-Up-Table to determine all edges that use a specific node.
    ConcreteEdge
    A ConcreteEdge linkes two nodes in the board graph via the properties speed, direciotn and doJump.
    CutOffCalculation
    Calculation Class to combine different cut off calculations.
    DeadlineReachablePointsCalculation
    Calculation object for calculating success and cut off ratings based on an initial player until a IDeadline is reached.
    EdgeImportance
    Calculation Class to calculate and combine the importance for ConcreteEdges.
    EnemyProbabilityCalculator
    Performs the SingleEnemyPrediction for each given player and combines the results.
    FloodFillPoint
    Helper class for flood filling the enemy minimum steps by storing a single point which has to be calculated into the minimum steps FloatMatrix.
    GradualReachablePointsCalculation
    Helper class to calculate ReachablePointsSingleThreaded.
    Graph
    A board that interprets the game as a graph.
    GraphCalculation
    Calculation object for calculating success and cut off ratings based on some initial players until a IDeadline is reached.
    GraphCalculator
    Calculator class calculating success and cut off ratings as ActionsRating objects and storing the last calculated results.
    IEdge
    Empty interface to generalize abstract and concrete edges
    IReachablePoints
    Interface for reachable points calculations.
    ISpeedSolver
    Interface for a solver that gets game information and returns a PlayerAction.
    LimitedQueue<Element>
    Class for storing multiple elements in a buffer.
    Node
    A cell of a board that holds information about all possible paths starting here.
    PredictivePlayer
    Player class which implements the IPlayer interface.
    RandomSolver
    A solver that sends a random action that doesn't cause instant suicide
    RatedPredictiveGraphPlayer
    RatedPredictiveGraphPlayer for success and cutting off enemies ratings, based on the graph board.
    RatedPredictivePlayer
    Class extending a PredictivePlayer with rating capability.
    ReachablePointsMultithreaded
    Calculator class calculating success and cut off ratings as ActionsRating objects and storing the last calculated results.
    ReachablePointsSingleThreaded
    Class implementing the IReachablePoints interface.
    ReachablePointsSolver
    Player implementing ISpeedSolver used for multiple SolverType values.
    ReachablePointsType
    Enum describing multiple types of the IReachablePoints calculation.
    SingleEnemyPrediction
    Calculates the enemy forward prediction for a single IPlayer.
    SlowDown
    Class to calculate a ActionsRating which prioritizes PlayerActions with a lower speed.
    SolverType
    SolverType enum representing multiple types of spe_ed solvers.
    SuccessCalculation
    Calculation Class to combine different success calculations
